# Compiled skill files and other transient artifacts
*.pyc
__pycache__/
*.tmp
.DS_Store

# Skill files that should NOT be committed
# (Hermes installs them via `hermes skills install <repo>` instead,
#  or by copying the SKILL.md to ~/.hermes/skills/ manually)
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/

# Keep SKILL.md tracked — that's the whole point of this repo.
# (Listed below explicitly so contributors don't accidentally .gitignore it.)
!SKILL.md